values:
Okay,

I have not posted to this account in about four years.&nbsp; I am extremely embarrassed by the layout of my account.&nbsp; Keep in mind that at the time I made this, I was in high school and had just come out.&nbsp; I was slightly over-enthused about the whole process, but I guess I had the right to be.&nbsp; It was a big deal, damn it!&nbsp; 

Well, I am now four years older and four years wiser (in some areas more than others).&nbsp; I have grown and matured in more ways than I can count, though I still procrastinate on homework, like right now. 

I think I'll start posting in here again just to see the differences (and similarities) in my life.&nbsp; I'll try to be a bit more detailed as to the events and why they made me feel certain emotions.&nbsp; I'll try to keep this updated often, but I can make no promises!&nbsp; 

....wow, I'm still embarrassed...Haha!
